
Helium
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Known issues:
- in certain themes not all element symbols are displayed correctly 
  (... instead of element symbol)
- there are still some glitches in the rotating
- the variable text of the undo toolbar icon makes the toolbar constantly 
  resizing
- the charge and implicit hydrogen heuristics are broken
- there seems to be a strange bug when the cmake build dir contains a dot;
  if this is the case, the bonds won't show in the molsKetch KPart
- the icon of a seperate methane molecule is not shown in the library


Upcoming releases
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Features:
- magnetic moving
- supporting different bond styles
- improved 3D rotating
